<div class="card card--vertical card--large-padding">

	<h1 class="card__title">Create an Account</h1>

	{{#if registrationSubmitted}}
		<h3>Thanks for registering.</h3>
		<p>You can now try to log in.</p>
	{{else}}
	<div class="form-intro">
		To request additional information, attend an event or join our newsletter subscriptions, please create an account, selecting the user type that best describes you. Please note that all new accounts will receive email updates from MARE. If you do not wish to receive these emails simply unsubscribe from our emailing list upon receipt.
	</div>
	<div class="form-intro">
		Prospective Families: We strongly recommend only creating one account <i>per family</i>. If you believe your family may already have an account established, please try any possible email addresses before creating a new account.
	</div>
	<div class="form-intro">
		Workers: If you are a Massachusetts social worker, you must create an account to register a child or family, RSVP for events, track inquiries and update your MARE caseload.
	</div>
	<div class="form-intro">
		Site Visitors: Feel free to browse the website without registering, you can always create an account at a later time.
	</div>
	<div class="form-intro">
	Please note that all new accounts will receive email updates from MARE about various services. If you do not wish to receive these emails simply unsubscribe from our emailing list upon receipt.
	</div>
	<div class="registration-type-selector-container">
		<select class="registration-type-selector" name="registration-type-selector">
			<option value="prospectiveParent" selected="selected">Prospective Parent</option>
			<option value="siteVisitor">Site Visitor</option>
			<option value="socialWorker">Social Worker</option>
		</select>
	</div>

	{{> registration-form-family}}
	{{> registration-form-site-visitor}}
	{{> registration-form-social-worker}}

	{{/if}}

</div>
